      "actor": "user",
      "content": "You are a planning subagent. Decompose the Hivemind Sidecar project into 6 executable phases following the GSD phase planning methodology.\n\n## Context\nRead these artifacts first (they contain the full architecture):\n1. `.hivemind/planning/sidecar-vision/landscape.md` — Task landscape, wave ordering\n2. `.hivemind/planning/sidecar-vision/ARCHITECTURE.md` — Full 1,113-line architecture design\n3. `.hivemind/planning/sidecar-vision/AUDIT-codebase-surfaces.md` — 85 integration surfaces\n4. `.hivemind/planning/sidecar-vision/RESEARCH-json-render.md` — json-render v0.19.0 API\n5. `.hivemind/planning/sidecar-vision/RESEARCH-nextjs.md` — Next.js 16 patterns\n6. `.hivemind/planning/sidecar-vision/RESEARCH-ecosystem.md` — Reference architectures\n\n## Phase Structure (6 phases, dependency-ordered)\n\nThe phases directories already exist:\n```\n.planning/phases/SC-01-sidecar-foundation/\n.planning/phases/SC-02-sidecar-rest-api/\n.planning/phases/SC-03-sidecar-nextjs-app/\n.planning/phases/SC-04-sidecar-session-explorer/\n.planning/phases/SC-05-sidecar-delegation-dashboard/\n.planning/phases/SC-06-sidecar-mems-control-panel/\n```\n\n## Each Phase Must Produce\n\nFor each phase, write a `{PHASE}-PLAN.md` containing:\n1. **Scope** — What this phase delivers\n2. **Dependencies** — What must be complete before this phase\n3. **Tasks** — Break down into executable tasks (numbered, actionable)\n4. **Deliverables** — Files created/modified, artifacts produced\n5. **Acceptance Criteria** — How to verify completion (EARS format preferred)\n6. **Risk Assessment** — Known risks and mitigations\n7. **Integration Points** — How this phase connects to adjacent phases\n8. **Gate Conditions** — What gates must pass (lifecycle, spec, evidence)\n\n## Phase Descriptions\n\n### SC-01: Foundation — Plugin HTTP Server + State Bridge\n**Purpose:** Implement SidecarServer class with Node http/ws, extend CANONICAL_PREFIXES in readonly-state.ts, lazy dependency registry, start server during plugin init. Bump json-render packages to 0.19.0, add next to optionalDependencies.\n\n### SC-02: REST API + Tool Proxy\n**Purpose:** Implement REST endpoints for all 27 tools (GET /api/state/:category, POST /api/tools/:name, GET /api/events SSE). Tool response wrapping. Port discovery via sentinel file. WebSocket for delegation streaming.\n\n### SC-03: Next.js 16 Standalone App\n**Purpose:** Initialize Next.js app in src/sidecar/app/, 4 panel routes, Server Components reading from plugin HTTP API, json-render catalog (44 components: 36 shadcn + 8 custom), SSE client-side integration, shadcn/ui setup.\n\n### SC-04: Session Explorer Panel\n**Purpose:** Session list, delegation tree visualization, session timeline, tmux pane visualization, live updates via SSE, search/filter capabilities.\n\n### SC-05: Delegation Dashboard Panel\n**Purpose:** Active/in-flight delegations, concurrency slots, completion status, notification history, dual-signal completion visualization, metrics/kpis.\n\n### SC-06: MEMS Browser + Control Panel\n**Purpose:** Knowledge graph navigation, decision anchors, trajectory + pressure visualization, config editor, tool inspector, command dispatch interface (invoke tools from browser).\n\n## Output Format\n\nFor each phase, write a PLAN.md in its directory:\n```\n.planning/phases/SC-01-sidecar-foundation/SC-01-PLAN.md\n.planning/phases/SC-02-sidecar-rest-api/SC-02-PLAN.md\n...\n```\n\nAlso write a dependency DAG:\n```\n.planning/phases/SIDECAR-DEPENDENCY-GRAPH.md\n```\n\nAnd a summary:\n```\n.planning/phases/SIDECAR-OVERVIEW.md\n```\n\nReturn: list of files created + dependency ordering summary.",
